short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds links on GW and FW store pages to browse related products

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Provides links on Games Workshop and Forge World product pages to browse the categories they belong to (such as product type, faction, unit type)

Because this extension requires a bundled data file, a different version is needed for each region of the stores. This version is for the en-NZ region.
